I think you can do this a little cleaner with [classnames](https://www.npmjs.com/package/classnames), which we already have:

```js
import cx from 'classnames';

let className = undefined;
cx('active-filters', className);  # 'active-filters'
className = 'some-class';
cx('active-filters', className);  # 'active-filters some-class';
```
